Details: Users can edit the name of the study.
Users can edit the description of the study.
Users cannot edit the Study Type,it will be External by default.
Users cannot edit the Access Level,it will be Read only by default.
Users can add or remove the tags for the study.
Users cannot edit the Bucket Name,it will have the same bucket name as the one used for study creation.
Users cannot edit this field,it will have the same value as the one used for study creation.
Users cannot edit the Prefix,it will have the same prefix as the one used for study creation.
Users cannot edit the Study Account,it will have the same project account as the one used for study creation.
Users cannot edit the Study Scope,it will have the same study scope as the one used for study creation.
Users can add or remove the project.
